ardson JTE (2011) The analysis of 2 x 2 contingency tables - Yet again. Sta=
tistics in Medicine 30:890.  <a class=3D"undecorated" href=3D"http://www.nc=
bi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21432882"><img src=3D"https://www.medcalc.org/common/=
